        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has thickened, transfer the meatballs and sauce to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> (or individual dishes)</p><p>Top with the<strong> torn mozzarella </strong>and put the dish in the oven for 10-12 min or until melted and bubbling – these are your <strong>cheesy meat-free meatballs</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>remaining balsamic vinegar</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and some <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>balsamic</strong> <strong>dressing</strong></p>",
