    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>ciabatta[s] </strong>in half, then add them to a baking tray and put in the oven for 1-2 min or until slightly toasted</p><p>Once slightly toasted, spread each slice with a little <strong>butter </strong>and top with the <strong>remaining garlic</strong>, then return to the oven for a further 3-4 min</p><p>Meanwhile, wash your <strong>lettuce </strong>and pat dry with kitchen paper, then tear into large bite-sized pieces</p>",
