      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>cheesy meat-free meatballs</strong> with the <strong>garlic ciabatta</strong> and<strong> torn lettuce</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>balsamic</strong> <strong>dressing</strong> over the lettuce</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
